Group Five to Lead Construction of Cape Town Rail Link, Business Day Says

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-06-17T05:23:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-17/group-five-to-lead-construction-of-cape-town-rail-link-business-day-says.html
Group Five Ltd. will be the lead
implementation agent in the construction of a rail link between
 Cape Town ’s central business district and the city’s airport,
Business Day reported, citing Passenger Rail Agency of South
Africa Executive Manager Dries van der Walt.  Construction could start sooner than the 2013 date set by
the Department of Transport, the Johannesburg-based newspaper
reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  